p/B0DJPLT4KJ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                        \u003c/p\u003e              \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe three-season collection is also available on DVD for $21 (was $45) with Amazon\u0026#39;s Prime Day deal. The DVD version doesn\u0026#39;t come with the Play Scene Pack, but you are still getting all 154 episodes across six discs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePrior to the Seasons 1-3 Blu-ray release, Bluey had only ever released on DVD. The three-season set on Blu-ray or DVD offers the best value, but you can buy each season on its own and the first two seasons in a combo pack. The Seasons 1-2 DVD edition is eligible for \u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-prime-day-movie-and-tv-best-blu-ray-deals/1100-6533045/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6533045\"\u003eAmazon\u0026#39;s B2G1 Free Sale\u003c/a\u003e on Blu-rays and DVDs. Additional coupon discounts are available for Seasons 1 and 2 on their own.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBluey on DVD:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Seasons-1-3-DVD-Various/dp/B0DJPLT4KJ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeasons 1-3\u003c/a\u003e -- $21 (\u003cdel\u003e$45\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Complete-Seasons-One-Two/dp/B0B29JSPV8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeasons 1-2\u003c/a\u003e -- $17.35 ($25) | \u003cem\u003eB2G1 Free\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Season-One-DVD/dp/B0BFBJ3TR8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeason 1\u003c/a\u003e -- $8.60 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Season-Two-Michael-Carrington/dp/B0BF6TG3WH?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeason 2\u003c/a\u003e -- $8.46 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Season-Three-Joe-Brumm/dp/B0CS12CTNV?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeason 3\u003c/a\u003e -- $10 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e                      \u003c/div\u003e   \u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4530675-blueyplayscene.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4530675\" data-ratio=\"0.5234375\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4530675-blueyplayscene.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4530675\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Bluey Seasons 1-3 - Play Scene Pack (Blu-ray edition bonus)\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4530675-blueyplayscene.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4530675-blueyplayscene.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/1595/15950357/4530675-blueyplayscene.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eBluey Seasons 1-3 - Play Scene Pack (Blu-ray edition bonus)\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-ref-id=\"2112\" data-template=\"2\" data-size=\"buylink__large\" data-title=\"[Various] Bluey: The Videogame\" data-collection=\"\" title=\"[Various] Bluey: The Videogame\"\u003e                  \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/1595/15950357/4194638-blueyvideogame.png\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                 \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Videogame-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0CJ3GM5CS?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Bluey-Videogame-Nintendo-Switch\\/dp\\/B0CJ3GM5CS?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;precap-vertical|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;precap-vertical|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Videogame-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0CJ3GM5CS?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" aria-label=\"Bluey: The Videogame for Nintendo Switch\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                              \u003c/p\u003e                                                              \u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eBluey fans can also save 50% on the \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Bluey-Videogame-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0CJ3GM5CS?tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eNintendo Switch edition of Bluey: The Videogame\u003c/a\u003e, which drops the price from $40 down to $20. Released in 2023, Bluey: The Videogame has the same animation style of the TV show and has its own story that plays like an interactive episode in the series. It supports local multiplayer for up to four players--Bluey, Bingo, Bandit, and Chilli are the playable characters--and has a collection of minigames from episodes of the show.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBefore you buy it, you may want to check out the upcoming Amazon-exclusive edition of Bluey: The Videogame. Outright Games is releasing a bundle for Nintendo Switch that includes a pair of adorable Gnome plushies inspired by the characters who live in the Heeler family\u0026#39;s garden. You can \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FGJZ7D64?tag=gamespot-preorders-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003epreorder Bluey: The Videogame Gnome Plush Bundle for $50\u003c/a\u003e ahead of its October 17 release.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere\u0026#39;s no shortage of Bluey interactive toys and activities, but a handful of the most exciting additions to the sprawling Bluey toy catalog arrived in stores on June 1: \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1\u0026amp;isPreview=1\u0026amp;asins=B0DRW8L7HY,B0DRW7Y7SV,B0DRW5PCBR,B0DRW5K9QH,B0DRW4WWVC\u0026amp;tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Bluey playsets\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e. The launch lineup features three Lego sets recommended for kids ages four and up and two Duplo playsets for toddlers. Check them out below:\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\n  \n                        \n    \n        \n        \n  \n                                  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n          \n  \n    \n          \n            \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eGot a news tip or want to contact us directly? Email \u003ca href=\"mailto:news@gamespot.com?subject=Hi GameSpot! I have a news tip for you!\"\u003enews@gamespot.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \n      \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n      \u003c/section\u003e\n    \n            \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n  \n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n                      \u003cmeta itemprop=\"seamless-content-list-items\" data-list-items=\"[{\u0026#34;guid\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1100-6521877\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;url\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\\/articles\\/babylon-5-complete-series-box-set-is-on-sale-for-its-best-price-ever\\/1100-6521877\\/\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;